  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nWhen chat from user appears in activity centre, even when all settings in Profile for both users are set to `Everyone` - `Everyone`, profile picture for this user will be not updated until adding this chat to home view and relogin.\r\nThis is applicable for all cases when a chat of new user appears in the activity center, the steps below are just the simplest way to reproduce.\r\nBy new user I mean: \r\n- you didn't have public chats before\r\n- you didn't open his profile and didn't add him to contacts\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) User A: set see profile pictures from `Everyone`, show profile pictures to `Everyone`\r\n2) User B: set see profile pictures from `Everyone`, show profile pictures to `Everyone`\r\n3) User A: start 1-1 chat with User B, send message\r\n4) User B: pay attention to activity centre\r\n\r\nPicture of User A remains unchanged until:\r\na) opening User A profile manually\r\nor\r\nb) opening chat with User A, relogin\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: RC 2 1.17 \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
